**🥽 VR APPLICATION CORE FEATURES**

**1. Scene Navigation & Exploration**
```
VR Navigation Controls:
├── Free Movement
│   ├── Walk/Run (joystick + button)
│   ├── Teleportation (point-and-click)
│   ├── Room-scale tracking (if hardware available)
│   └── Comfort settings (snap turn, vignette)
├── Camera Controls
│   ├── Zoom in/out (pinch gesture)
│   ├── Pan (drag gesture)
│   ├── Rotation (head movement)
│   └── Viewpoint saving/loading
└── Evidence Access
